reviews.review:
As a Bioshock fan I'm somewhat confused if I liked this game or not, why? I'll tell you.

The Positives:

+ The game looks great and the cenario is original;
+ The shooting is fluid and fun;
+ The story is good;
+ You don't need to play previous titles to play this game;
+ New Plasmids.

The Negatives:

- Choises don't have consequences;
- You can only equip 2 weapons at any time;
- No Hacking, no Camera mechanic, no Big Daddy ( or something similar);
- The game feels linear most of the times.

I feel that this game removed some of the unique aspects that the previous titles brought to the table, but at the end of the day I recommend this game for Elizabeth and her character alone, I got to congratulate her voice actor for bringing such a joy and life to this game.
